skins.shipDescription: Atlanta-class Light Cruiser ¨C San Diego, Hull Number CL-53!
skins.selfIntroduction: I'm San Diego! I've heard I'm second only to Enterprise for the most stars earned! ... I don't really know what a "star" is, but it sounds cool! What is it, Commander? ... A-merry-car? Is that some kind of secret code?
skins.acquisition: Hello~! I'm San Diego, the cruiser who earned the most stars in World War 2! Hehe, that's it for my introduction! I'm just too good!
skins.login: Hey, Commander, let's have an exciting water gun fight!
skins.details: What's so interesting about this stuff? Let's go play instead~!
skins.secretaryIdle1: Apparently people come looking for me after they've planted apple seeds... am I some kind of harvest god or something?!
skins.secretaryIdle2: Battle stars? Are they really that amazing? I thought everyone had some?
skins.secretaryIdle3: Come on, get motivated, now! Sit around like this and you'll go dumb!
skins.secretaryTouch: Hey, what are you looking for?
skins.secretarySpecialTouch: Hey, not so fast you pervert!

skins.shipDescription: Heheh~¡î I have no idea what just happened, but I feel like I've gotten super strong! Commander, can you see my sparkly aura~?
skins.acquisition: Heheh~¡î I have no idea what just happened, but I feel like I've gotten super strong! Commander, can you see my sparkly aura~?
skins.login: Hey, Commander! Let Super-Smart Sandy handle all your work for today! It'll be done before you can say "no thanks"!
skins.secretaryIdle1: Let's have a race, Commander! I'll be both your opponent and the referee!
skins.secretaryIdle2: Lalala la la~! Sing along with me, Sara!
skins.secretaryIdle3: You look bummed out, Commander~ How about we turn that frown right upside down?
skins.secretaryTouch: Can you feel my smartifying sparkly aura too, Commander~?

skins.shipDescription: Commander, with the power of your love, San Diego is sure to become number one in this port! ...Number one in what? I'm not really sure myself, but I'll definitely make it happen!
skins.acquisition: Commander, with the power of your love, San Diego is sure to become number one in this port! ...Number one in what? I'm not really sure myself, but I'll definitely make it happen!
skins.login: I've already finished today's work and did it all in a flash! Now c'mon, it's time to have fun!
skins.details: Is my June bride look just the bestest or what!
skins.secretaryIdle1: So, Commander! You mind having tonight's dinner microwaved? Is the bath at 50 degrees all cool with you? Don't answer, 'cause San Diego went and did it all already!
skins.secretaryIdle2: Man, San Juan's such a worrywart~ I'll be just fine, 'cause I've got you, Commander! Everything's gonna be right as rain!
skins.secretaryIdle3: I'll cheerlead for you, Commander! Hip, hip, hooray! One, two, three! Whoop-de-doo!

skins.shipDescription: Merry Christmas! Super idol San Diego, making her dazzling debut! Commander, you must come to my performance! ...Venue?! What's that?
skins.acquisition: Merry Christmas! Super idol San Diego, making her dazzling debut! Commander, you must come to my performance! ...Venue?! What's that?
skins.secretaryIdle1: That's strange, why's the microphone cord getting shorter and shorter?
skins.secretaryIdle2: I don't really get it, but if I work hard, it'll be A-O-K!
skins.secretaryIdle3: Commander, wanna sing a few songs as well? Ehehe, here, here! Wooaahh! (CRASH) W-who tripped me?
skins.secretaryTouch: The smartest person is the one who is the happiest! Ehehe, that's why San Diego is the smartest!
